<br>
You can and will be sued for lots of cash for hurting a persons eardrums or ruining their hearing in any way. <br>
<br>
A guy next to me on my next to last day there ended up losing his hearing in both ears by over 70% due to an air horn and he won a huge lawsuit. I don't know the amount but he won hands down and the company footed the attorney fees too. You = 1 attorney  Telemarketing Company = several attorneys.<br>
<br>
All other ploys are fair game in my eyes. <br>
<br>
sure getting off the call lists or onto no call lists are effective but no fun. <br>
<br>
have fun but don't do physical damage.<br>
<br>
