<br>
Say &quot;could you excuse me for just one moment, I have to get the kids out of the tub,&quot; wait a few moments, then scream &quot;AHHHHH!! MY BABY!!!!&quot;.. just hope the poor telemarketer doesn't have a weak heart hehe<br>
<br>
Pretend that you're on the verge of suicide and that no one likes you, don't let them talk about their product, but instead keep talking about yourself and make up all sorts of problems that you might have, etc, and if they try to hang up on you tell them that they're the last straw and if they hang up, you are going to kill yourself.. see how many hours you can keep them on the phone <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Try to have phone sex with them (best results are if you're both male)<br>
<br>
Feign interest in the product and ask ANY question you can possibly think of and take as much of their time as you possibly can, then tell them that you arn't allowed to make any financial decisions and he must talk to your financial manager, you'll transfer him... hand the phone to a friend who repeats the entire process of asking every single question that they possibly can think of, then say &quot;this isn't my department, you'll need to talk to the person in charge of (whatever)&quot; and hand the phone to another friend who makes them repeat everything again.. keep up this sherade as long as you want to or untill they hang up.<br>
<br>
Ok those are just a few that I could think of... hehe<br>
