<br>
We do get lots of people with clipboards ringing our doorbell, and I've come up with a new technique to deal with them. Instead of answering the door and then having to get rid of them, I walk to where I can clearly see through a window if it's a neighbor or someone else we know, and if it's not, I don't even answer the door. Mind you, they can clearly see that someone is home and has just checked them out and decided to ignore them. *grin* <p>-Itienne Sleepstealer, 63 chanter, &ltSans Requiem&gt, Xev<br>
